| Plot                    = Spider-Man sends out his bio-engineered spider to find recruits to help his battle against villiany. The spider finds two boys named Stan and Lee as well as the [[You|viewer]]. They, along with the viewer, get recruited by Spider-Man, and together, they go to Spider-Man's base. In the base, Spider-Man trains them by teaching them his battle moves. Later, Spider-Man's [[Spider Sense]] warns him that Venom is terrorizing the town. Together, Spider-Man and the new recruits defeat Venom.

| Cast                    = 

| Notes                   = * The video uses footage from [[Spider-Man: The Animated Series]].
* The first names of Stan and Lee are a clear reference to Spider-Man's co-creator, [[Stan Lee]].
* While most of the video is in live-action, the Venom fight sequence is 3D animation.
